citation.case_name: Gaona-Tovar v. United States and Duarte-Juarez v. United States

html_with_citations:
544 U.S. 902

GAONA-TOVAR
v.
UNITED STATES; and
DUARTE-JUAREZ
v.
UNITED STATES.

No. 04-8322.

Supreme Court of United States.

March 7, 2005.

1

C. A. 5th Cir. Reported below: 110 Fed. Appx. 438 (first judgment) and 461 (second judgment). Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted, judgments vacated, and cases remanded for further consideration in light of United States v. Booker, 543 U.S. 220 (2005).
